title: Dissapointed
review:
I came to see this after watching Midsommar, a movie I did like a lot.
But this one, Hereditary, was such a dissapointment to me. I would not recommend to anyone, there's nothing here you haven't seen before.

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode VII - The Force Awakens
title: A bad movie with a lot of budget
review:
Big budget couldnt save this, its bad.
Is the first and only Star Wars movie I saw so far for which I was constantly checking how much time is left.
